    "causal_summary": "Codex.app and Claude Code can leave MCP helper stacks alive after respawns or session stops, producing linear RAM growth on this workstation. This packet adds a dry-run-first process sweeper, chains a repo-local Claude Stop cleanup command into the existing hook, and teaches the three MCP servers to exit after configurable idle time.",
